---
// CTA Section - Apply
---

<section class="bg-brand-accent py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
        Ready to stop winging it?
      </h2>

      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white mb-12 opacity-95">
        Reply with what's not working. I'll tell you straight if I can help.
      </p>

      <button
        class="bg-white text-brand-accent hover:bg-gray-100 font-bold py-4 px-12 text-lg transition-all duration-200"
        onclick="window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('daisy:open'))"
      >
        Apply Now
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
